    "description": "Look who's finally decided to wake up.<br><br><br><br>In NeverHome, a young girl named Granger suddenly awakens in a world that's not her own. Brave through a hostile world using only your wits and the help of new friends you make along the way to return to your reality.<br><br>Explore liminal and abstract series of rooms as you solve puzzles and search for the truth of these never-ending halls. You might even encounter interesting secrets along the way. But be aware: these halls are not empty– they never were.<br><br><br><br>NeverHome - Hall of Apathy is the first chapter in a larger anthology-style game, inspired by RPG Maker horror games from the early 2010's. Expect it to take at least a few hours to complete.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384310/extras/7ce7915129d24ffd00cd5e6b7b4260b6.poster.avif?t=1767762169\" width=170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384310/extras/7ce7915129d24ffd00cd5e6b7b4260b6.webm?t=1767762169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>A minor warning</strong>: This game is a horror game. As such, it contains minor amounts of blood and other unsettling imagery.<br><strong>Epilepsy warning</strong>: This game contains some scenes with flashing or bright images. Viewer discretion is advised.",
